XhD2s%3D&h=2151b74d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vZg5e6qcgz0</a></blockquote><br />\n佢成日都咁講，話啲議員明知問題係太多人，但為左保住個位個個都唔提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97086ce3a24f70c5c419969fa93fee1473c60fb","tid":154923,"uid":52933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:09:06.000Z","msg":"呢d非洲國家d人自己都唔夠食仲生咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b95ab1706de7925199f78059004209c68d1355","tid":154923,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"淨係掛住仆野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b8fc2c81753d68908cc6adaa197af4c1f2aae6","tid":154923,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:16:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲劣質人種好難幫<br />\n除非俾西方國家殖民三百年"},{"pid":"b913c69b171019418b72de67fb6ddac08b671c70","tid":154923,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/de/cf/41/decf41b9a342c7f3c758616f025629f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2Fde%2Fcf%2F41%2Fdecf41b9a342c7f3c758616f025629f9.jpg&h=70a6a3e3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\njoan d畫真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又準備黎香港開畫展啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時開？好想見下真跡作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}